"outputs":[],"properties":{"text":""},"widgets_values":["KSampler 简介\n在 Stable Diffusion 中，KSampler 是一个用于生成图像的关键节点。它通过将随机噪声转换为与文本提示相匹配的图像来实现图像生成。KSampler 是 ComfyUI 中一个重要的组成部分，可让用户控制和定制图像生成过程。\n\nKSampler 的工作原理\nKSampler 采用迭代过程来生成图像。在每个迭代步骤中，它会根据以下因素更新图像：\n\n文本提示: 通过 CLIP 模型编码的文本描述\n模型输出: 来自 Unet 模型的潜在空间表示\n随机噪声: 用于确保图像多样性的随机元素\nKSampler 使用各种技术来提高图像质量和生成效率，包括：\n\n引导扩散: 逐步将随机噪声转换为与提示相匹配的图像\n降噪: 逐步去除噪声以锐化图像\n超分辨率: 提高图像分辨率"],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653"},{"id":10,"type":"Note","pos":[-121,-381],"size":[2539.0478515625,143.15992736816406],"flags":{"pinned":false},"order":5,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"properties":{"text":""},"widgets_values":["Target: Use ReV Animated model generate some images for learning."],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653"},{"id":7,"type":"CLIPTextEncode","pos":[460,600],"size":[612.33203125,88],"flags":{"collapsed":false,"pinned":true},"order":12,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"name":"clip","localized_name":"clip","label":"clip","type":"CLIP","link":5}],"outputs":[{"name":"CONDITIONING","localized_name":"CONDITIONING","label":"CONDITIONING","type":"CONDITIONING","links":[6,22],"slot_index":0}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.3.24","Node name for S&R":"CLIPTextEncode"},"widgets_values":["(nude, thighs, cleavage:1.3), 3d, cartoon, anime, sketches, (worst quality, bad quality, child, cropped:1.4) ((monochrome)), ((grayscale)), (rating_safe), (score_3_up, score_4_up, score_5_up, monochrome, vector art, blurry), worst quality, low quality, nsfw, nude,",[false,true]]},{"id":12,"type":"Note","pos":[460,410],"size":[617.3935546875,88],"flags":{"pinned":true},"order":6,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"title":"正向提示词","properties":{"text":""},"widgets_values":["杰作，摄影，获奖，想象一下一个狼蛛的特写镜头，它复杂的花纹和毛茸茸的腿清晰地呈现在焦点中。这只食鸟蜘蛛栖息在一片叶子上，每一个捕猎姿态的细节都被精确地捕捉到。它的眼睛在昏暗的光线下闪闪发光，露出准备捕猎的毒牙。背景模糊，使得人们的注意力集中在狼蛛的强大存在和即将到来的捕猎紧张感上。8k, 16k, 32k，逼真摄影"],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653"},{"id":35,"type":"Note","pos":[459,-22],"size":[601.1466674804688,106.22654724121094],"flags":{},"order":7,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"properties":{"text":""},"widgets_values":["A detailed, photorealistic image of a cute hamster eating, masterpiece, award-winning photography, imagine a close-up shot of the hamster with its tiny paws holding a piece of food, its whiskers twitching and its eyes sparkling with curiosity. The texture of its fur is soft and fluffy, with intricate details in every strand. The background is blurred to highlight the hamster's adorable expression and focused action. 8k, 16k, photorealistic, high detail, natural lighting"],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653"},{"id":36,"type":"Note","pos":[461,-180],"size":[601.751953125,106.5099868774414],"flags":{},"order":8,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"properties":{"text":""},"widgets_values":["Masterpiece, Photography, award winning, Imagine a close-up shot of a tarantula, its intricate patterns and hairy legs sharply in focus. The bird-eating spider is poised on a leaf, every detail of its predatory stance captured with precision. Its eyes glisten in the dim light, and its fangs are visible as it prepares to hunt. The background is blurred, drawing attention to the tarantula's formidable presence and the tension of the impending hunt.8k, 16k, 32k, photorealistic"],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653"},{"id":6,"type":"CLIPTextEncode","pos":[460,240],"size":[622.5296020507812,121.95561981201172],"flags":{"collapsed":false,"pinned":false},"order":11,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"name":"clip","localized_name":"clip","label":"clip","type":"CLIP","link":3}],"outputs":[{"name":"CONDITIONING","localized_name":"CONDITIONING","label":"CONDITIONING","type":"CONDITIONING","links":[4,21],"slot_index":0}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.3.24","Node name for S&R":"CLIPTextEncode"},"widgets_values":["Masterpiece, Photography, award winning, Imagine a close-up shot of a tarantula, its intricate patterns and hairy legs sharply in focus. The bird-eating spider is poised on a leaf, every detail of its predatory sta